name: jamotools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "jamotools" %}
{% set version = "0.1.10" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: "b3dc212ae4fc8dd63ec3ab666c98a6390ac5d28d0adba356ed89360c2d2fb115"

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 2
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - future
    - numpy
    - python
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - jamotools
    - jamotools.jamo
    - jamotools.vector

about:
  home: "https://github.com/HaebinShin/jamotools"
  license: "GPL-3.0"
  license_family: "GPL"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "A library for Korean Jamo split and vectorize."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - dcunn
    - adbeda
    - oblute
    - rluria14
